{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"0fb810ae4b","title":"七律.长征","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"badb0f3faa","index":0,"year":1935,"month":10,"day":null,"articleId":"0fb810ae4b"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji7-2","name":"毛泽东全集第7卷(2)","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives8/main/mao-quanji/maoquanji7-2.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji7-2":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"f5defb9f2f","type":"paragraph","text":"七律.长征（1935年10月）红军不怕远征难，方水千山只等闲。五岭透逸腾细浪，回","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji7-2","articleId":"0fb810ae4b"},{"id":"768ebb30cd","type":"paragraph","text":"乌蒙磅磷走泥丸。","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji7-2","articleId":"0fb810ae4b"},{"id":"902aff6fcc","type":"paragraph","text":"[1]七律，七言律诗的简称。七律是律诗的一种，每篇一般为八句，每句七个字；偶句末一字押平声韵，首句末字可押可不押，必须一韵到底；句内和句间要讲平瓜，中间四句按常规要用对仗。","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji7-2","articleId":"0fb810ae4b"},{"id":"8291dd1930","type":"paragraph","text":"[2]长征，1934年10月间，中央红军主力从中央革命根据地出发作战略大转移，经过福建、江西、广东、湖南、广西、贵州、四川、云南、西康、甘肃、陕西等十一省，击溃了敌人多次的围追和堵截，战胜了军事上、政治上和自然界的无数限险，行军二万五千里，终于在1935年10月到达陕北革命根据地。这首诗和《念奴娇·昆仑》《清平乐·六盘山》都是在长征取得胜利时所作的。","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji7-2","articleId":"0fb810ae4b"},{"id":"4b7a1e28d1","type":"paragraph","text":"[3]五岭透腾细浪，大庚、骑田、萌猪、都庞、越城等五岭，绵延（“透”）于江西、湖南、广东、广西四省之间。1934年10月，中央红军从福建、江西出发，沿这四省边境的五岭山道，越过敌人封锁线，向西进军。“腾细浪”是说险峻的五岭绵延起伏，在红军眼中只像水面吹起的细小波浪。","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji7-2","articleId":"0fb810ae4b"},{"id":"d14da54256","type":"paragraph","text":"[4]乌蒙磅磷走泥丸，乌蒙山绵延在贵州、云南两省之间，气势雄伟福","index":5,"publicationId":"maoquanji7-2","articleId":"0fb810ae4b"},{"id":"fe7e38ce5c","type":"paragraph","text":"H","index":6,"publicationId":"maoquanji7-2","articleId":"0fb810ae4b"},{"id":"d66eb6cfb9","type":"paragraph","text":"好","index":7,"publicationId":"maoquanji7-2","articleId":"0fb810ae4b"},{"id":"57c9f28a67","type":"paragraph","text":"皖心","index":8,"publicationId":"maoquanji7-2","articleId":"0fb810ae4b"},{"id":"6852088bec","type":"paragraph","text":"中","index":9,"publicationId":"maoquanji7-2","articleId":"0fb810ae4b"},{"id":"53431dcd48","type":"paragraph","text":"","index":10,"publicationId":"maoquanji7-2","articleId":"0fb810ae4b"},{"id":"74c71de20c","type":"paragraph","text":"经","index":11,"publicationId":"maoquanji7-2","articleId":"0fb810ae4b"},{"id":"6928188db3","type":"paragraph","text":"B","index":12,"publicationId":"maoquanji7-2","articleId":"0fb810ae4b"},{"id":"00ae1f5a1c","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东手书《七律·长征》30《红军不怕远征难万水千山只等闲》（油画）","index":13,"publicationId":"maoquanji7-2","articleId":"0fb810ae4b"},{"id":"b0e116c9f7","type":"paragraph","text":"发，维系","index":14,"publicationId":"maoquanji7-2","articleId":"0fb810ae4b"},{"id":"7c6a90177f","type":"paragraph","text":"中《红军不怕远征难》（诗意画）《万水千山只等闲》（油画）","index":15,"publicationId":"maoquanji7-2","articleId":"0fb810ae4b"},{"id":"c49e4f7754","type":"paragraph","text":"线4wNci","index":16,"publicationId":"maoquanji7-2","articleId":"0fb810ae4b"},{"id":"0a7b1b82e9","type":"paragraph","text":"《红军不怕远征难》（诗意画）《万水千山只等闲》（油画）《万水千山只等闲》（诗意画）特健有财来东横大名传我设在欢","index":17,"publicationId":"maoquanji7-2","articleId":"0fb810ae4b"},{"id":"d65f94cca8","type":"paragraph","text":"大","index":18,"publicationId":"maoquanji7-2","articleId":"0fb810ae4b"},{"id":"040d661023","type":"paragraph","text":"镜大《大渡桥横铁索寒》（诗意画）《更喜山千里雪》（油画）欢2唐望日山帆喜更公福源3","index":19,"publicationId":"maoquanji7-2","articleId":"0fb810ae4b"},{"id":"140cb1772c","type":"paragraph","text":"武司谷《更喜山千里雪》（诗意画）《更喜眠山千里雪》（诗意画）《三军过后尽开颜》（油画）平过后尽开有《三军过后尽开颜》（诗意画）《万里征程诗不尽》（油画）","index":20,"publicationId":"maoquanji7-2","articleId":"0fb810ae4b"},{"id":"49cddfdb4d","type":"paragraph","text":"清福8","index":21,"publicationId":"maoquanji7-2","articleId":"0fb810ae4b"},{"id":"30f3be7e56","type":"paragraph","text":"《长征》（诗意画）毛上清